A meal that most of the kids in her class seemed to like was sukiyaki ( Sukiyaki is a Japanese dish that is prepared and served in the nabemono style. She was currently making some tea, boiling water with the kettle and preparing the tea leaves for when it was done. She turned the stove up to the highest setting because she wanted the water to boil quickly. But even now it was taking forever...

'Alright. We got another being in here. I have to play everything safely just to make sure that I'm safe.' Before anything, she washes her hands. Anyways, time to see what this person is all about. It would be a lie to say that she isn't curious. "...Hello?"
